<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #00466a;">Xuthority</h2>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em;">
            Hi <%= userName %>,
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            Your password for your <strong>Xuthority</strong> account has been successfully changed. This change was made on <strong><%= changeDate %></strong>.
        </p>

        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #155724; font-weight: bold;">
                âœ… Password Change Confirmed
            </p>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            If you made this change, you can safely ignore this email. If you didn't change your password, please contact our support team immediately as your account may have been compromised.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            For security reasons, we recommend:
        </p>
        <ul style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666; margin-left: 20px;">
            <li>Using a strong, unique password</li>
            <li>Enabling two-factor authentication if available</li>
            <li>Regularly reviewing your account activity</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 10px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #aaa;">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> Xuthority. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 